{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"073f69cd42","title":"关于拟在三峡游泳给中央的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"637aae0a82","index":0,"year":1957,"month":7,"day":7,"articleId":"073f69cd42"}],"tags":[{"id":"8b05ac46d8","name":"王任重","type":"人物"},{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji38","name":"毛泽东全集第38卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/38-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji38":{"comments":[{"id":"764ba9d05b","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"073f69cd42","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"罗瑞卿，当时任公安部部长。王任重，当时任中共湖北省委第一书记。"},{"id":"f10ddbf7fd","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"073f69cd42","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中共中央政治局常委1957年7月7日给毛泽东复电说，关于在三峡游泳一事，常变提出先派人调查和试水，然后再作决定。后来，根据试水情况，中央常委没有同意。"},{"id":"8aead4a1a1","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"073f69cd42","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"孙勇，当时任中共中央办公厅警卫处警卫科副科长。韩队长，指韩庆余，当时任中央警卫团一中队中队长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"00a7f748ff","type":"title","text":"关于拟在三峡游泳给中央的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"073f69cd42"},{"id":"764ba9d05b","type":"paragraph","text":"中央，并请转罗瑞卿、王任重”二同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"073f69cd42"},{"id":"f10ddbf7fd","type":"paragraph","text":"我拟七月廿四日到重庆，廿五日乘船东下，看三峡。如果峡间确能下水，则下水过三峡，或只游三峡间有把握之一个峡。如不可能，则于船出峡口时下水到宜昌，或径到沙市。然后乘船到武汉。此事，已与瑞卿谈过。请中央考虑批准。如果中央同意的话，则（一）请瑞卿即带孙勇、韩队长等能游者十人左右，到武汉与已试航试泳一次之船队再去试行，反复几次。（二）王任重同志不要去，我拟于七月中句到武汉和省委谈一些问题。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"073f69cd42"},{"id":"8aead4a1a1","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"073f69cd42"},{"id":"b9799e290f","type":"paragraph","text":"七月七日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"073f69cd42"}],"page":{"id":"68f8bf8a28","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"073f69cd42","start":155,"end":155}}}},"__N_SSG":true}